pageContext.claim: “A lot of votes came too late. I've already decisively won many critical states, including massive victories in Florida, Iowa, Indiana, Ohio, to name just a few. We won these and many other victories.”
pageContext.analysis: Again, Trump says that votes that were not counted on Election Day should not count. But some key swing states, such as Pennsylvania, could not start counting mail or absentee ballots until Election Day because of rules set by GOP lawmakers.
